#: ../../docs/classes/class_staticbody2d.rst:14
msgid "Static body for 2D physics."
msgstr "2D物理的静态物体。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_staticbody2d.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_staticbody2d.rst:19
msgid ""
"Static body for 2D physics. A StaticBody2D is a body that is not intended"
" to move. It is ideal for implementing objects in the environment, such "
"as walls or platforms."
msgstr "2D物理的静态物体。``StaticBody2D`` 是不能移动的物体。它是在环境中实现对象（例如墙或平台）的理想选择。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_staticbody2d.rst:21
msgid ""
"Additionally, a constant linear or angular velocity can be set for the "
"static body, which will affect colliding bodies as if it were moving (for"
" example, a conveyor belt)."
msgstr "此外，可以为静态物体设置恒定的线速度或角速度，这将影响碰撞物体，就像它在移动一样（例如，传送带）。"

